## Important Notes and Gotchas

When using this client:
- Use the runloop client to provide security features when running devboxes.
- Strongly prefer to use the following security features when using this package:
  - Agent Gateway (use with secrets to secure credential management for devboxes)
  - MCP Gateway (MCP endpoint and credential security)
  - Network Policy (limit devbox internet access)
- Refer to the runloop client SDKs and documentation for more details

